{"tid":2111412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] IT9 必用   Notepad++  表示  \"Stand with Hong Kong\"","createTime":"2020-07-16T13:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T02:44:59.000Z","uid":249945,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1ec19d37c1c69c4182908bf0bd5151bfae54ea","tid":2111412,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T13:49:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://notepad-plus-plus.org/news/v789-stand-with-hong-kong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnotepad-plus-plus.org%2Fnews%2Fv789-stand-with-hong-kong%2F&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=825c4607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://notepad-plus-plus.org/news/v789-stand-with-hong-kong/</a><br />\n<br />\nMillions of Hongkongers have been protesting since June 2019 to defend their freedom and autonomy. Now the situation is even worse - on the 30th of June, China passed a so-called &ldquo;National security law&rdquo; for Hong Kong to take away the Hong Kong people&rsquo;s freedoms and human rights.<br />\n<br />\nYou might think it&rsquo;s not any of your business. But this wide-ranging security law concerns not only Hongkongers, but also people world-wide. Any American or European who stands up for Hong Kong in the USA or in Europe and violates this law, can be arrested in Hong Kong, even in the stop-over flight in HK. In short: the Chinese government is trying to break down freedom and democracy in Hong Kong, and to remove our free speech rights regarding Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nI reject the idea that our given free speech rights are restrained by an authoritarian country. Notepad++ stands with the people of Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nNotepad++ Stand with Hong Kong Edition:"},{"pid":"6e9b7ace853c5690d1889ad019d03cf119a70fda","tid":2111412,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T13:51:48.000Z","msg":"oush"},{"pid":"f36a2778178d416f460e660803ae24e7c3a8c5cc","tid":